{"title": "Flatland: A Romance of Many Dimensions (version 3)", "description": "In Flatland: A Romance of Many Dimensions\u2014written by Edwin Abbott Abbott\u2014readers are presented with a question. What if the world were flat? Well and truly flat, that is, with figures in place of humans as we would think of them. It takes this question, and pushes it further, asking about the natures of people, and society, as well as angles, lines, and the dimensions of space itself. It takes this question, and uses it to deliver insightfully political satire, and a surprising amount of mathematical education. - Summary by FlamboyantOtter", "duration": 11779, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "9567", "name": "Edwin Abbott Abbott"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/flatland3_2603_librivox/flatland_2603.jpg", "copyright_year": "1884", "genres": ["Action & Adventure Fiction"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "LibriVox Volunteers"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "MaybeCordelia"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Rapunzelina"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Larry Wilson"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "PREFACE TO THE SECOND AND REVISED EDITION, 1884. BY THE EDITOR", "readers": [13225], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/flatland3_2603_librivox/flatland_00_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 627}, {"section": 1, "title": "Dedication, and Of the Nature of Flatland", "readers": [13225], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/flatland3_2603_librivox/flatland_01_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 357}, {"section": 2, "title": "Of the Climate and Houses in Flatland", "readers": [13225], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/flatland3_2603_librivox/flatland_02_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 373}, {"section": 3, "title": "Concerning the Inhabitants of Flatland", "readers": [13225], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/flatland3_2603_librivox/flatland_03_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 623}, {"section": 4, "title": "Concerning the Women", "readers": [13225], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/flatland3_2603_librivox/flatland_04_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 878}, {"section": 5, "title": "Of our Methods of Recognizing one another", "readers": [13225], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/flatland3_2603_librivox/flatland_05_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 827}, {"section": 6, "title": "Of Recognition by Sight", "readers": [13225], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/flatland3_2603_librivox/flatland_06_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 803}, {"section": 7, "title": "Concerning Irregular Figures", "readers": [14580], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/flatland3_2603_librivox/flatland_07_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 387}, {"section": 8, "title": "Of the Ancient Practice of Painting", "readers": [14580], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/flatland3_2603_librivox/flatland_08_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 326}, {"section": 9, "title": "Of the Universal Colour Bill", "readers": [14580], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/flatland3_2603_librivox/flatland_09_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 418}, {"section": 10, "title": "Of the Suppression of the Chromatic Sedition", "readers": [14580], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/flatland3_2603_librivox/flatland_10_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 483}, {"section": 11, "title": "Concerning our Priests", "readers": [14580], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/flatland3_2603_librivox/flatland_11_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 326}, {"section": 12, "title": "Of the Doctrine of our Priests", "readers": [14580], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/flatland3_2603_librivox/flatland_12_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 552}, {"section": 13, "title": "How I had a Vision of Lineland", "readers": [14580], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/flatland3_2603_librivox/flatland_13_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 489}, {"section": 14, "title": "How I vainly tried to explain the nature of Flatland", "readers": [14580], "path": "http